Title: De Power of Death
Description:
De trial can't be stopped after it starts, but we won't let Tzadah use our people or our loa to aid Mueh'zala.

If we be doing nothing, even more Darkspear could be swayed to find power in Mueh'zala. I'll look for a way to breach Tzadah's protective energy, you stop the spirits from taking over our home!
